ir future needs and desires Cosmetologist requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Cosmetologist requirements High School diploma or equivalent Must hold a valid cosmetology license Excellent customer service skills and able to follow their requests Must have a minimum of 1 year of experience working in a salon setting Possess a positive attitude and great communication skills Should have an interest in and aptitude for sales Cosmetologist related job titles: Licensed Cosmetologist Esthetician/Cosmetologist Esthetician Nail Technician Wax Specialist Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
